&lt;p&gt;How do I remove a specific value from an array? Something like:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-js s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-javascript&quot;&gt;array.&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-title function_&quot;&gt;remove&lt;/span&gt;(value);  &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot;&gt;// removes all elements with value&lt;/span&gt;
